A man who murdered his fiancée with a single punch during an argument over whether to take a bus or a taxi home was jailed for life today.

Former soldier Ryan Ingham, 26, sent Caroline Finegan, 29, crumpling to the ground like a ‘bag of potatoes’ after he ran at her at full pelt before striking her in the face.

One witness was ‘moved to tears’ after seeing Ingham hit her ‘like a car travelling at 40mph’ before he started to shake her ‘like a rag doll’ as she lay on the ground in an act of ‘wanton thuggery’.

