2005: Criminal assault - during course of argument with his 17-year-old girlfriend, he punched her in the face and body causing minor injury.

August 2005: Same victim. Ingham elbowed her in the head during a domestic argument and received a suspended sentence.

August 2008: Assaulted mother and father.

2012: Threatened girlfriend at the time with a knife to the neck and threatened her unborn child.

October  2012: Before he became engaged to Caroline Finegan, there was incident where he hit her and she sustained a swollen cheek.

